{"tid":2312784,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨軍於旺角食肆「桔梗」檢地盤頭盔、疑似伸縮棍及標語 兩負責人被捕","createTime":"2020-12-05T08:58:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T12:25:23.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ef35aa73c0efb900303ce0e155293423a91a6b70","tid":2312784,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T08:58:49.000Z","msg":"警方於旺角食肆「桔梗」檢頭盔伸縮棍標語 兩負責人被捕<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，昨晚在旺角一帶地舖及樓上酒吧採取反罪惡行動期間，到砵蘭街食肆「桔梗」調查有否違反限聚令，在餐廳一個無上鎖房間，發現1支懷疑伸縮棍、15個頭盔、15個防毒面罩及一些印有標語的橫額，以涉嫌「管有違禁武器」及「藏有工具可作非法用途」，拘捕兩名分別25歲及29歲的餐廳負責人，兩人獲准保釋，下月上旬向警方報到。警方未有交代橫額寫有甚麼內容，在展示證物時亦未展示有關橫額。<br />\n<br />\n另外，警方搜查「桔梗」期間，有市民在店外聚集，其中一名男子戴上面具，並披上寫有抗爭口號的黑色旗幟，被警員帶走。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的餐廳在社交網站表示，負責人下午會向記者交代事件。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2369427\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2369427&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w8yZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=bb29a1fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2369427</a>"},{"pid":"eb3acadb72fdcb012639d89e4ca1189bc3062911","tid":2312784,"uid":57513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T09:03:01.000Z","msg":"又屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b685b3ddd97de72c18bd4f9da99f6362439e96","tid":2312784,"uid":50386,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T09:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N0H41LY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN0H41LY.jpg&h=83c7f3ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全部都係隔離新填地街買到嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc0cace8dc50d2fbf41c6ea0f6fd24d939f1883f","tid":2312784,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T09:11:34.000Z","msg":"唔好癲啦死黑警"},{"pid":"df88fabb6dcd325a3759dffff4a2a8053d085665","tid":2312784,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020